trans-unit.source: Enables the server to gather information on the capabilities of the browser that is running on the client.
trans-unit.target: Gjør det mulig for serveren for å innhente informasjon om funksjonene i leseren som kjører på klienten.

trans-unit.source: The HttpBrowserCapabilities properties are accessible through the <xref:System.Web.HttpRequest.Browser%2A> property of the ASP.NET intrinsic <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Request%2A> object.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapene HttpBrowserCapabilities er tilgjengelig via den <xref:System.Web.HttpRequest.Browser%2A>for ASP.NET indre <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Request%2A>objektet.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Request%2A> </xref:System.Web.HttpRequest.Browser%2A>

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.HttpBrowserCapabilities"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.HttpBrowserCapabilities"> </xref> klasse.
